WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.021
Video is the most engaging tool you have. The customer sees your face,

00:00:04.071 --> 00:00:08.091
sees their car, and hears your voice — it is the closest thing

00:00:08.141 --> 00:00:12.162
to standing next to them in the bay. Use it for inspections, recommendations,

00:00:12.212 --> 00:00:13.414
and showing completed work.
